      <title>由于需求担忧超过中东供应担忧，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-dip-demand-concerns-outweigh-middle-east-supply-fears-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三早盘油价下跌，原因是中国经济势头疲软以及美国近期降息希望减弱对全球需求的担忧超过了中东紧张局势加剧带来的供应担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-dip-demand-concerns-outweigh-middle-east-supply-fears-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 01:20:37 GMT</pubDate>
